  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/8dea28846251f6a4e1aab165969cdcd0.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A perspective-shifting puzzle game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Find the Keys</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Collect the Tapes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Switch Gravity </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Over 100 levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/9efb5fcd6d96a9c3f0302dbd16adca46.poster.avif?t=1774217429\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/9efb5fcd6d96a9c3f0302dbd16adca46.webm?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/9efb5fcd6d96a9c3f0302dbd16adca46.mp4?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Axyz is a vaporwave-flavoured tribute to 90s cult classic <strong>Kula World</strong>. Use your environmental and spacial awareness to find the key, reach the exit and beat the level. Replay levels as many times as you want to collect everything and record your best time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/2d2d6a3fb2dbf58080453ae3bd551b05.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/0cb639a00528741323855a13e83de827.poster.avif?t=1774217429\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/0cb639a00528741323855a13e83de827.webm?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/0cb639a00528741323855a13e83de827.mp4?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level has 5 tapes to collect in any order, providing an optional challenge for those wishing to push themselves to the limits. Find as many as you can to unlock more levels that provide a greater challenge and reach for 100% completion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/aee37e7f182934992d8f5df31d706200.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/7bf61e944065dfe203eb6a186b3addd9.poster.avif?t=1774217429\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/7bf61e944065dfe203eb6a186b3addd9.webm?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/7bf61e944065dfe203eb6a186b3addd9.mp4?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some items can only be reached by switching gravity. Levels will often have multiple ways to beat it and switching gravity if often the key. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/0cc87dbc5339309834e60701eea00177.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/b98a6b906ab3cb77e3a0d5c85a4660ee.poster.avif?t=1774217429\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/b98a6b906ab3cb77e3a0d5c85a4660ee.webm?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/b98a6b906ab3cb77e3a0d5c85a4660ee.mp4?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 100 mind-bending levels across 8 worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/667f8b8cd402921ad9623c5ce88b9b0d.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mixtape soundtrack featuring Pizza Hotline, Major Axis, CAIMANS, and many more.  Encompassing Drum and Bass, Breakbeat, Synthwave, and more to create an energetic and dreamlike soundtrack.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/8dea28846251f6a4e1aab165969cdcd0.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A perspective-shifting puzzle game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Find the Keys</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Collect the Tapes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Switch Gravity </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📼 Over 100 levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/9efb5fcd6d96a9c3f0302dbd16adca46.poster.avif?t=1774217429\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/9efb5fcd6d96a9c3f0302dbd16adca46.webm?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/9efb5fcd6d96a9c3f0302dbd16adca46.mp4?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Axyz is a vaporwave-flavoured tribute to 90s cult classic <strong>Kula World</strong>. Use your environmental and spacial awareness to find the key, reach the exit and beat the level. Replay levels as many times as you want to collect everything and record your best time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/2d2d6a3fb2dbf58080453ae3bd551b05.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/0cb639a00528741323855a13e83de827.poster.av