ea00177.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/b98a6b906ab3cb77e3a0d5c85a4660ee.poster.avif?t=1774217429\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/b98a6b906ab3cb77e3a0d5c85a4660ee.webm?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/b98a6b906ab3cb77e3a0d5c85a4660ee.mp4?t=1774217429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 100 mind-bending levels across 8 worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850490/extras/667f8b8cd402921ad9623c5ce88b9b0d.avif?t=1774217429\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mixtape soundtrack featuring Pizza Hotline, Major Axis, CAIMANS, and many more.  Encompassing Drum and Bass, Breakbeat, Synthwave, and more to create an energetic and dreamlike soundtrack.</p>",
